<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965075>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Morphological structures of head.A—Archiearis notha; B—A. parthenias; C, E—Cleta jacutica; D, F—Holarctias rufinaria; G—Scopula ornata. A, B, D—antennae of males; C, F—head, frontal view; E—lateral view; G—dorsal view; f. w.—frons width; d. e.—diameter of eye." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7965075/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965077>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Wing venation. A—Jodis putata; B—Geometra papilionaria; C—Hemithea aestivaria; D—Chlorissa viridata; E—Holarctias rufinaria; F—Rhodostrophia vibicaria; G—Scopula ornata; H—Timandra rectistrigaria; I—Cyclophora albipunctata. A–D—hindwings; E, F—forewings; G–I—right pair of wings. R veins marked in red, M veins marked in blue, Cu veins marked in green, areole marked in teal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7965077/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965172>
    dc:description "FIGURE 31. Adults of Siberian Sterrhinae. A—Lythria purpuraria; B—Rhodostrophia jacularia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7965172/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965139>
    dc:description "FIGURE 22. Adults of Siberian Sterrhinae. A—Idaea aversata; B—I. straminata; C—I. descitaria; D—Holarctias rufinaria." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7965139/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965143>
    dc:description "FIGURE 23. Adults of Siberian Sterrhinae. A—Holarctias rufinularia; B—Scopula agutsaensis; C—S. immorata; D—S. corrivalaria." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7965143/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7965161>
    dc:description "FIGURE 29. Adults of Siberian Sterrhinae. A—Scopula aequifasciata; B—S. cajanderi; C—S. albiceraria; D—Cyclophora albipunctata." ;
